weka.classifiers.evaluation

Class Kendall

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.classifiers.evaluation.AbstractEvaluationMetric
      • weka.classifiers.evaluation.Kendall
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, StandardEvaluationMetric

    public class Kendall
extends AbstractEvaluationMetric
implements StandardEvaluationMetric
    Provides Kendall's tau rank correlation coefficient for evaluating regression schemes. Implementation taken from Quan Sun's Fantail project. More info at: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kendall_rank_correlation_coefficient
    Version:
    $Revision: 1 $
    Author:
    Felipe Bravo-Marquez (fjb11@students.waikato.ac.nz)
    See Also:
